Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.cmput301f17t27.nume.account.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An object instantiated from this class represents a user's profile. With this object alone you have everything you need to display information to the user
